OL,7,FSouthern Water has experienced an
OL,8,Fissue while it works to restore the
OL,9,Favailability of water to the Hastings
OL,10,Farea following a burst water main.
OL,12,FThe water utility company say: "As we
OL,13,Fcontinue our work restoring the
OL,14,Favailability of water to the Hastings
OL,15,Farea from the previous burst, we're
OL,16,Fcurrently experiencing an issue in our
OL,17,Fnetwork that has affected Fairlight
OL,18,FReservoir, meaning its water level is
OL,19,Flower than normal.
