OL,7,F"To keep supplies running and meet
OL,8,Fdemand, we're bringing in extra water
OL,9,Fthrough a tankering operation.
OL,11,F"As an additional precaution, we'll be
OL,12,Fsetting up a bottled water station and
OL,13,Fwill share its location as soon as
OL,14,Fit's ready ` we would urge customers
OL,15,Fnot to turn up to any bottled water
OL,16,Fstation before we announce their
