OL,3,CSouthern Water experience issue on
OL,4,CChristmas Day while working to restore
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FTania Flasck, Director of Water
OL,8,FOperations, said: "We know this is
OL,9,Fworrying news, especially on Christmas
OL,10,FDay, and we want to reassure our
OL,11,Fcustomers that we're doing everything
OL,12,Fpossible to restore normal levels at
OL,13,FFairlight Reservoir.
OL,15,F"We'd also ask everyone in Hastings
OL,16,Fand the wider area to use water
OL,17,Fcarefully where they can. This will
OL,18,Fhelp us refill the reservoir more
OL,19,Fquickly and reduce the risk of any
OL,20,Fsupply interruptions."
